00:55:04.635 --> 00:55:05.552
Quoi?

00:55:06.094 --> 00:55:06.970
Voleur de salaire ?

00:55:07.054 --> 00:55:08.680
Oui, un voleur de salaire.

00:55:08.764 --> 00:55:11.725
